Select Ebene1,Ebene2,Ebene3,Ebene4,Artikel_nr,sum(Liefermenge) as Menge from (SELECT p.Ebene1, p.Ebene2, p.Ebene3, p.Ebene4, p.Artikel_Nr, p.Liefermenge as Liefermenge FROM GERAETE AS g WITH(NOLOCK) INNER JOIN POSITIONEN AS p WITH(NOLOCK) ON g.IDNR = p.IDNR AND g.ServiceEbene1 = p.Ebene1 AND g.ServiceEbene2 = p.Ebene2 AND g.ServiceEbene3 = p.Ebene3 AND g.ServiceEbene4 = p.Ebene4 inner join artikel a WITH(NOLOCK) on p.artikel_nr=a.artikelpart_nr WHERE p.Ebene1 = :1 AND p.Ebene2 = :2 AND p.Ebene3 = :3 AND p.Ebene4 = :4 and Artikel_Nr>'' and p.Auft0Rep1W2AL3AL3=1 and (p.Zuordnung<>'M' and p.Zuordnung<>'A' and p.Zuordnung<>'W' and p.Zuordnung<>'K') and a.Ebene1=:5 and a.Ebene2=:6 and a.Ebene3=:7 and a.Ebene4=:8 and g.Artikelnummer=':9'
UNION all
SELECT p.Ebene1, p.Ebene2, p.Ebene3, p.Ebene4, p.Artikel_Nr, p.Liefermenge as Liefermenge FROM GERAETE AS g WITH(NOLOCK) INNER JOIN POSITIONEN AS p WITH(NOLOCK) ON g.IDNR = p.IDNR AND g.Ebene1 = p.Ebene1 AND g.Ebene2 = p.Ebene2 AND g.Ebene3 = p.Ebene3 AND g.Ebene4 = p.Ebene4 inner join artikel a WITH(NOLOCK) on p.artikel_nr=a.artikelpart_nr WHERE p.Ebene1 =:1 AND p.Ebene2 = :2 AND p.Ebene3 = :3 AND p.Ebene4 = :4 and Artikel_Nr>'' and p.Auft0Rep1W2AL3AL3<=0 and (p.Zuordnung<>'M' and p.Zuordnung<>'A' and p.Zuordnung<>'W' and p.Zuordnung<>'K') and a.Ebene1=:5 and a.Ebene2=:6 and a.Ebene3=:7 and a.Ebene4=:8 and g.Artikelnummer=':9'
) as AGGREGATE group by Ebene1,Ebene2,Ebene3,Ebene4,Artikel_nr order by sum(Liefermenge) desc
select distinct ebene1,ebene2,ebene3,ebene4, WW_REP_LINK.WW_Auftrag from ww_rep_link WITH(NOLOCK) where Ebene1=:1 and Ebene2=:2 and Ebene3=:3 and Ebene4=:4 and WW_REP_LINK.Rep_Auftrag_Nr=:5
